data.name: lb_Welcome_2.Text
data.value:
Connecting Dropbox has the following benefits:
1. Automatically backup recent files to dropbox for further use.
2. When your Waveface Station is unreachable, you can still access recent files in Waveface from Dropbox. Click “Next” to start the process and enjoy the benefits now. Or “Skip” to do it later.

data.name: lb_Welcome_1.Text
data.value: Waveface can Connect to Dropbox to provide you more features!

data.name: lb_SetupCompleted_2.Text
data.value:
The setup process has been completed.
You can enable the connection between Waveface and Dropbox later in the Preference panel.
Or Click "Try Again" to try out the connection process again.
Enjoy Waveface with full gears and start connecting your digital life.

data.name: lb_Linkage_1_2.Text
data.value:
First, you need to log in your dropbox account to proceed.
Click "Connect" and we will open the Dropbox webpage for you using your web browser.
After you log in, please follow the instruction provided by dropbox to make the connection.

data.name: lb_InstallDropbox_1_2.Text
data.value:
You need to install Dropbox to proceed.
Click "Install Dropbox" and we will open the Dropbox webpage for you using your web browser.

data.name: lb_Linkage_2_2.Text
data.value:
Already done? Awesome!
Now, click "Verify" to start verifying your connection between Waveface and Dropbox.

data.name: lb_InstallationFailed_2.Text
data.value: We can’t find the Dropbox installed on this computer. Click "Install Dropbox" to start the installation process and connect to Dropbox now. Or "Skip" to do it later.

data.name: lb_InstallationFailed_1.Text
data.value: Oops! You haven’t installed Dropbox yet!

data.name: lb_ConnectionSuccessfully_2.Text
data.value: Waveface and Dropbox has been successfully configured! Enjoy Waveface with full gears and start connecting your digital life.

data.name: lb_Verifying_1.Text
data.value: Verifying the connection between Waveface and Dropbox

data.name: lb_ConnectionFailed_2.Text
data.value:
The Connection between Waveface and Dropbox was not successful.
Click "Try Again" to connect to Dropbox again, or "Skip" to do it latter.

data.name: lb_InstallDropbox_2_2.Text
data.value: After successfully installing, click "Continue" to proceed.
